title: Compliance Officer Interview
Application Type: I applied online. I interviewed at LaunchGood in Jul 2022
Interview Descriptions: Although it was quite positive interview, I haven’t received feedback for one month and their talent acquisition does not respond. Quite unprofessional approach. First they had reached out to me for this role and then they don’t respond.

title: Design Fellow Interview
Interview Descriptions: Meeting with CDO, then with VP of Design. The interview process took 2-3 weeks, with a specific start-date pinned. Showed me samples of what the design work currently consisted of and asked my opinion on the matter.
Interview Questions: How would you organize our design documentation?

title: Software Engineer Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 3 months. I interviewed at LaunchGood (New York, NY) in May 2022
Interview Descriptions: The first round was introduction interviews and going through your resume. Then a second round of technical interviews regarding JavaScript and algorithm-related questions, similar to what you would do on leetcode. Then, the third round of behavioral questions.
